So if I am deploying Lambda using build.gradle first time with TAG A then its working fine (By first time I mean when I am creating a new Lambda) and tag is being applied and I can see that on AWS Console. But when I am re-deploying it again by adding another tag &quot;TAG B&quot; then the new tag is not being applied and it is not updating the existing Lambda tags. Any idea or suggestion what I am doing wrong? Thanks

